  <summary>11/15/2007--Introduced.
Property Tax Fairness Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow an additional standard tax deduction in 2007 or 2008 (available to taxpayers who do not itemize) for state and local real property taxes; and (2) include within the reporting requirements of investment brokers the adjusted basis of any security owned by customers of such brokers.</summary>
